2+1.name: MORNINGSTAR
2+1.sig_info: Morningstar’s weapon grants her a link to her Opponent’s Soul, allowing her to siphon away a portion of the power from any Fury, Power Gain, or Regeneration Buffs they trigger, reducing their potency by 25 to 50.01%, and granting her her own Buff.
